OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1780506355
OL,3,CAutistic children lacking support as
OL,4,Ccouncils 'fail to meet demand'
OL,6,FMothers of children with additional
OL,7,Fneeds in Gwynedd say that shortages of
OL,8,Fsocial workers and support services
OL,9,Fare placing significant stress on
OL,10,Ffamilies.
OL,12,FLeian Roberts from Penrhyndeudraeth,
OL,13,FGwynedd, has a nine-year-old son named
OL,14,FTwm who is non-verbal and autistic. Ms
OL,15,FRoberts, 46, is a qualified nurse and
OL,16,FTwm's father is a paramedic.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/20
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1780506355
OL,3,CAutistic children lacking support as
OL,4,Ccouncils 'fail to meet demand'
OL,6,FHowever Ms Roberts told current
OL,7,Faffairs programme Y Byd ar Bedwar that
OL,8,Fwhen Twm was six years old, she had to
OL,9,Fgive up her full-time work in order to
OL,10,Ftake care of her son.
OL,12,F"People ask, 'What's challenging?'
OL,13,FLife as a whole is challenging," she
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,FLocal authorities are responsible for
OL,17,Fsocial care services for both adults
OL,18,Fand children within their areas.
OL,26,@uD@`O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/20
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1780506355
OL,3,CAutistic children lacking support as
OL,4,Ccouncils 'fail to meet demand'
OL,6,FGwynedd Council, who oversee the area
OL,7,Fwhere Ms Roberts and Twm live, say
OL,8,Fthey and other local authorities
OL,9,F"continue to fail to meet the demand"
OL,10,Ffor ALN support despite significant
OL,11,Finvestment.
OL,13,FMs Roberts is eligible for 10 hours a
OL,14,Fweek of support from a carer, while
OL,15,FTwm is also able to attend the Hafan y
OL,16,FSer respite centre in Penrhyndeudraeth
OL,17,Fonce every fortnight. The centre
OL,18,Fprovides short-term care for children
OL,19,Faged eight to 18 with additional needs
OL,20,Facross Gwynedd and Anglesey.
OL,26,@xD@Bsr
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/20
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1780506355
OL,3,CAutistic children lacking support as
OL,4,Ccouncils 'fail to meet demand'
OL,6,FShe said: "I don't think it's enough
OL,7,Fat all.
OL,9,F"In an ideal world, I'd like to see
OL,10,Fhim going there once a week, because I
OL,11,Ffeel like I need that respite for my
OL,12,Fmental health. And it is to have a
OL,13,Frest because you don't stop - it's
OL,14,Frelentless."
OL,16,FMs Roberts believes Gwynedd Council do
OL,17,Fnot understand the pressures families
OL,18,Fwith additional learning needs face.
OL,20,F"They're not aware of the situation,"
OL,21,Fshe said.
OL,26,@nD@KOUqD@AOUvD@LO]|D@AOU|D@eO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/20
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1780506355
OL,3,CAutistic children lacking support as
OL,4,Ccouncils 'fail to meet demand'
OL,6,F"They need to listen to us. When
OL,7,Fparents say there's a problem, they
OL,8,Fneed to listen.
OL,10,F"There's no price tag on giving care
OL,11,Fto somebody like Twm, and they need to
OL,12,Flook at where they're investing and
OL,13,Fwhere they're lacking, and clearly the
OL,14,Fcare for children with additional
OL,15,Fneeds is lacking."
OL,17,FTwo other mothers from Gwynedd, Kim
OL,18,FAdams Williams and Chloe Galvin, who
OL,19,Falso have children with additional
OL,20,Flearning needs, said they too face
OL,21,Fstruggles with support.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@RO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/20
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1780506355
OL,3,CAutistic children lacking support as
OL,4,Ccouncils 'fail to meet demand'
OL,6,FBoth said they have no social workers,
OL,7,Fdue to a lack of staffing.
OL,9,F"It's quite frustrating, because who
OL,10,Felse do we have to call? It's nothing
OL,11,Fdisrespectful to the social workers,
OL,12,Fbut they're so stretched, they don't
OL,13,Fhave the staff," said Ms Adams Willams.
OL,15,FSince 2016, there has been a 42
OL,16,Fpercent drop in the number of people
OL,17,Fapplying for traditional social work
OL,18,Fqualifying courses.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/20
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1780506355
OL,3,CAutistic children lacking support as
OL,4,Ccouncils 'fail to meet demand'
OL,6,FWales also has fewer social workers
OL,7,Fthan any other country in the United
OL,8,FKingdom.
OL,10,F"The system is broken"
OL,12,FThe mothers say children with
OL,13,Fadditional needs urgently require
OL,14,Fbetter-funded support services.
OL,16,F"There's more children requiring these
OL,17,Fservices, but the services are getting
OL,18,Fsmaller. It's just not enough," Ms
OL,19,FAdams Williams said.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/20
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
