PN,46708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1780506355
OL,3,CAutistic children lacking support as
OL,4,Ccouncils 'fail to meet demand'
OL,6,FMs Roberts added: "I don't think they
OL,7,Fhave an insight into what families
OL,8,Flike us live day to day."
OL,10,FThe Welsh Government estimates that
OL,11,FASD (autistic spectrum disorder)
OL,12,Faffects 1 in 100 people.
OL,14,FDr Rebecca Williams is a Consultant
OL,15,FClinical Psychologist with over 25
OL,16,Fyears experience working with autistic
OL,17,Fchildren and adults across the NHS and
OL,18,Fin private practice, specialising in
OL,19,Fautism and ADHD assessments.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/20
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
